data.description: Built in 2020, this immaculate South facing ranch has a fresh, modern interior!  Enjoy the spacious open layout & timeless color palette. The kitchen features rich cabinetry, quartz counters, stainless steel appliances & tiled backsplash that will become the perfect place to prepare family meals and entertain.  Relax in the luxurious primary bath with a dual vanity, quartz countertops and a spacious walk-in closet. The finished lower level offers an extra bedroom, bath, expansive family room and a large storage area for creating your ideal recreation area for indoor activities.  Step outside to the large covered deck and enjoy entertaining or just relaxing in the large fenced yard. A walkable neighborhood, close to all the amenities,  walking distance to schools and minutes from 730 acres of recreational space at Flanagan Lake with a 220 acre lake & a 5-mile hiking/biking trails. Seller offering $10,000 for buyers closing costs. AMA
